snippet.textDisplay: This song brings a lot of memories from my days in Rajasthan. While I appreciate the flamboyance, this song lacks some heart, I was waiting for the Marwari beats to drop but that never happened, those who heard this OG Marwari song they will know what I am talking about. Definitely need some change in the creative department. I guess take some cues from Coke Studio Pakistan. Remember it's not just about the visual elements, we need to work on the music as well.
snippet.textOriginal: This song brings a lot of memories from my days in Rajasthan. While I appreciate the flamboyance, this song lacks some heart, I was waiting for the Marwari beats to drop but that never happened, those who heard this OG Marwari song they will know what I am talking about. Definitely need some change in the creative department. I guess take some cues from Coke Studio Pakistan. Remember it's not just about the visual elements, we need to work on the music as well.
